{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2187002, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这里的我们 包括我吗", "timestamp": 1627828913, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187004, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "虽然左壬不会听，但是及时认识到这一点对自己有帮助，而不至于成为扛旗的人的炮灰", "timestamp": 1627828919, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187021, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "改造成某些人进步的工具，而不是我们", "timestamp": 1627829083, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187026, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一边骂中特搞资本主义一边称赞资本主义本身属于是精神分裂", "timestamp": 1627829129, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187042, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在数轮树洞论战中，左壬已经就共产主义道德的可行性提出了各种各样观点", "timestamp": 1627829281, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187044, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "虽然各种观点并不完全相容", "timestamp": 1627829297, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187047, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这倒也是客观事实", "timestamp": 1627829302, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187057, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "至今没有看到左壬内部的共识，也没有可证明的理论，不足以说服我", "timestamp": 1627829386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187060, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187021, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 本人一以贯之不相信共产主义。有些人一边骂资本主义，一边无视中途搞资本主义 ，属于左右互搏了", "timestamp": 1627829406, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187064, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187021, "tag": null, "text": "Alice发言我是没想到的，脑洞奇大，我认为是偷换概念了，还没想好怎么回应", "timestamp": 1627829469, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187069, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187021, "tag": null, "text": "另外更正一下，这位youtuber是“悉尼奶爸”，推荐给大家", "timestamp": 1627829521, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187082, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187044, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave:从道德入手阐释资本主义和共产主义无疑是一种理论贫困", "timestamp": 1627829607, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187088, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187002, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我只能这样空泛的回应：每个时代，自由都面临着四大挑战：强人对权力集中的渴望，穷人对财富不均的怨恨，无知者对乌托邦的向往，无信仰者将自由和放纵混为一谈。", "timestamp": 1627829676, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187097, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187082, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不从道德入手很难说明共产主义革命为什么要“立刻发生”，以及何以可能“立刻发生”", "timestamp": 1627829778, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187088, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: \n#134065 哈哈我发过", "timestamp": 1627829792, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187097, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 从历史上生产力更替来看，一定是先进生产力逐步替代落后生产力实现的，其中每一个人都是自在的而非自为的，道德，他有几个师？", "timestamp": 1627829886, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187131, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187042, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 一个直观的例子，左壬常说工人管工厂，搞鞍钢宪法的好，那么这个好一定能体现在生产力优越上，可以是利润率高，可以是生产成本低，但是能满足这些条件的工人直管工厂的例子在全球大概就一个手指头数的过来", "timestamp": 1627830153, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187131, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 这个你好像说的不对，他们常用的是掀桌子玩法，既不谈利润也不谈成本", "timestamp": 1627830197, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187138, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 那不更烂了吗", "timestamp": 1627830224, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187150, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187141, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 神奇的是，在恰当的假设下（比如引入“道德”），这一套东西逻辑上好像是没有问题的。。。", "timestamp": 1627830283, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187157, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187141, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 指并不至于出现逻辑不自洽的尴尬场面", "timestamp": 1627830302, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187162, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187138, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 空泛地从道德入手试图灵魂深处闹革命、在几代人的生命周期里改造人性，这本身就是歧路，历史已经证明了行不通", "timestamp": 1627830353, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187170, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": 2187157, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 在这些人的理论当中当然是一个逻辑闭环，但是实践嘛....", "timestamp": 1627830394, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2187673, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《经济学原理》刚翻三分之一的时候我也这么想", "timestamp": 1627835533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2188133, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 423769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "苏联笑话说的很透彻，就是“我们要不惜一切代价xxx”那一个", "timestamp": 1627853626, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 423769, "reply": 25, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "“共产主义之所以不行，是因为每个人都是self-interest，每个人都是greedy，而我最欣赏资本主义的地方在于它把人最坏的地方改造成我们进步的工具”    ——油管youtuber“细腻奶爸”最新一期节目中一个普通话说的很好的外国人的观点", "timestamp": 1627828836, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631248852, "url": "", "vote": {}}}